These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, fuchsia
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Color   | fuchsia  | aquamarine |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, teacher
1. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Job      | teacher     | security-guard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
City: nizza, venice
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| City   | nizza | venice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite
2 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite | fanta   |
| Pet       | chinchilla | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, salsa
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | ambient    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, d&b
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry
1. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | d&b     |
| Cigar   | blend | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
