.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-19::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, june
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |
| Pet     | lizard  | turtle    |
| Birthday   | june | november |

